{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.520", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.160", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine lieben Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.240", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe mich sehr dar\u00fcber gefreut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.880", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir auf die Anregung der CDU/CSU-Bundestagsfraktion hin in diesem Deutschen Bundestag eine breite Mehrheit hinbekommen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.080", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um einen solchen Antrag vorzulegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.240", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Anlass war, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.280", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Opferbeauftragte der Bundesregierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.680", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der fr\u00fchere Ministerpr\u00e4sident Beck, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "heute seinen Bericht vorlegt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.960", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber der Anlass war auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.800", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir in der letzten Legislaturperiode mit einer Reform der Opfer\u00adentsch\u00e4digung leider nicht so vorangekommen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.360", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir es uns eigentlich vorgenommen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.120", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Nahles. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.840", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen hat dieser Antrag zwei Elemente. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.640", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum einen wollen wir uns mit der Frage besch\u00e4ftigen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was m\u00fcssen wir tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.440", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit die Opfer von Gewalt durch Terrorismus richtig entsch\u00e4digt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.280", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wie geht man mit ihnen richtig um? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.440", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum anderen m\u00fcssen wir aber auch klar sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.480", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass trotz eines Opferentsch\u00e4digungsgesetzes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.520", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das es in kaum einem anderen Land der Welt so gibt wie bei uns, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.360", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "noch immer Opfer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.240", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die nicht Opfer von Terror, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.040", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern von Gewaltkriminalit\u00e4t in unterschiedlichster Form geworden sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.320", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht angemessen entsch\u00e4digt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.160", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich h\u00e4tte mir gew\u00fcnscht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.240", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir im selben Atemzug, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in dem wir diesen Antrag heute vorlegen und Vorschl\u00e4ge machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.920", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch die Einsetzung eines Untersuchungsausschusses zum Fall Amri h\u00e4tten beschlie\u00dfen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.120", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Anregung f\u00fcr die Einsetzung eines Untersuchungsausschusses habe ich nicht erst vor 14\u00a0Tagen gemacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.000", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern schon vor l\u00e4ngerer Zeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.200", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unmittelbar nach dem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.600", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was am Breitscheidplatz passiert ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.880", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "habe ich gesagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.360", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss genau untersucht werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.400", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn es best\u00e4rkt nat\u00fcrlich nicht das Vertrauen in den Rechtsstaat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.200", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn so viele Pannen auf einmal in einem einzigen Fall passiert sind wie im Fall Amri."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.720", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen diesen Untersuchungsausschuss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.120", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um zu wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.400", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was passiert ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.880", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber vor allem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.720", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um daraus die richtigen Schl\u00fcsse zu ziehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.600", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich kann nur sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.720", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was man als Erstes sp\u00fcrt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.960", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn es tats\u00e4chlich so war, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.840", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Zusammenwirken der verschiedenen Beh\u00f6rden auf Landes- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.880", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Bundesebene zu diesen Problemen gef\u00fchrt hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.600", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann kann man nicht sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.240", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eWir \u00e4ndern nichts daran\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.800", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor allem nicht dann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.680", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn der Bundesinnenminister sagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.000", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen uns \u00fcber die Sicherheitsarchitektur noch einmal ernsthaft Gedanken machen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.920", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da sind L\u00e4nder und der Bund gefragt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.600", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor diesem Hintergrund w\u00fcrde ich dringend dazu raten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.720", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass keiner sagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.000", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist unser Kompetenzbereich.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.400", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den Menschen und vor allem den Opfern ist es ziemlich egal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.480", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wer zust\u00e4ndig ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.560", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Funktionieren muss es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.800", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.800", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und daran haben wir Zweifel."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.360", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege Kauder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.120", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lassen Sie eine Zwischenfrage zu?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.240", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.480", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was den Opferschutz angeht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.160", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "finde ich schon: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.480", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So dramatisch die Situation der Opfer von Terror ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.960", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so dramatisch ist f\u00fcr die Frau, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.520", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die vergewaltigt worden ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.000", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch der Angriff auf ihre k\u00f6rperliche Unversehrtheit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.440", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist es richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.160", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir heute nicht nur der Opfer von Terrorismus gedenken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.080", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.040", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Opferschutz muss f\u00fcr alle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.120", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Opfer von Gewalttaten geworden sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.760", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verbessert werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.000", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu seiner ersten Rede rufe ich den Kollegen Roman Reusch von der AfD auf."
   ]
  }
 ]
}